  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.header": "使用地址路由流体包裹",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_1": "仓库",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_2": "当在流体打包机上放置告示牌时……",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_3": "→ 仓库",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_4": "打包完毕的流体包裹将会携带一行写有其地址的文字",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_5": "包裹过滤器根据流体包裹地址制定它们的路线",
