  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_8": "→ 工厂",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_9": "工厂",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_10": "流体包裹经过动力锯后会被直接销毁",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_11": "除过滤器外，货物蛙港和邮箱亦可以指定流体包裹路线",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager_address.text_12": "查看它们的思索界面来了解它们的行为",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.header": "流体打包和拆解流体包裹",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_1": "流体打包机可以将流体储罐中的流体打包成流体包裹",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_2": "接入红石信号，它会从储罐中提取流体并打包进流体包裹",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_3": "流体包裹可以被捡起，也可以进行运输，就像其他任何物品一样",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_4": "放入流体打包机的流体包裹将被拆解，而流体将被注入到流体储罐中",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_5": "已满",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_packager.text_6": "流体打包机无法接收无法完全拆卸的流体包裹",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.header": "使用流体传输器转移流体",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.text_1": "流体传输器可以将流体从一个容器转移到另一个容器",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.text_2": "并且，流体传输器可以通过设置过滤来限制允许通过流体",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.text_3": "此外，流体传输器会被红石信号禁用",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.text_4": "当然，流体传输器还可以像这样连接",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.fluid_transporter.text_5": "注意，流体传输器无法像这样侧向连接",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.header": "设置动力注液枪",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_1": "动力注液枪需要先分配注液目标",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_2": "手持动力注液枪右击传送带、置物台或其他元件来选择目标",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_3": "再次右击已选择的目标可以移除该选择",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_4": "放置后，动力注液枪会保存之前选择的所有目标",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_5": "动力注液枪会将底部流体容器作为流体源",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_6": "动力注液枪可以同时管理范围内的多个注液目标",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_7": "不是所有容器都可以直接交互",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.mechanical_fluid_gun_setup.text_8": "在此情境下可以通过流体舱口或多流体接口让这些容器成为注液目标",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.header": "使用多流体存取端口存取流体",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_1": "在对多流体容器进行存取有时会比较麻烦",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_2": "多流体存取端口可以将流体容器延伸以方便存取",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_3": "多流体存取端口最多同时向三个方向存取流体",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_4": "并且，可以分别为三个方向配置过滤",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_5": "此外，多流体存取端口还可以被红石信号禁用",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_6": "注意，多流体存取端口无法链式连接",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.multi_fluid_access_port.text_7": "不过，一个流体容器可以同时连接多个多流体存取端口",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.faucet.header": "使用水龙头填充物品",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.faucet.text_1": "水龙头可以对物品进行注液",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.faucet.text_2": "并且，水龙头会根据物品智能注液",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.faucet.text_3": "注意，水龙头无法为传送带上的物品注液",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.faucet.text_4": "此外，水龙头还可以向部分流体容器注入流体",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.smart_faucet.header": "使用智能龙头填充物品",
  "fluidlogistics.ponder.smart_faucet.text_1": "智能龙头可以对物品进行注液",
